      "question": "How does someone pirate a movie?&nbsp; <!----><!----><!---->",
      "answer": "<p data-path-to-node=\"0\" id=\"p-rc_c61cc9533ace422d-19\"><span class=\"citation-25 citation-end-25\">At a high level, movie piracy is the unauthorized copying, distribution, or streaming of copyrighted films.<source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c213414374=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c213414374=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"1\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span> From a technical and operational standpoint, the process generally breaks down into two main phases: <b data-path-to-node=\"0\" data-index-in-node=\"209\">sourcing</b> the video and <b data-path-to-node=\"0\" data-index-in-node=\"232\">distributing</b> it.<sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3754498845=\"\">  <source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3754498845=\"\" _nghost-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"></source-inline-chip></sources-carousel-inline></p><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container luminous-sources hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button multiple-button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"Genaue Quellenangaben für Zitat aus Aiplex Anti-Piracy ansehen. Öffnet die Seitenleiste.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_5f824f32d3c5e2d6&quot;,&quot;c_3721b541fcdb6876&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c61cc9533ace422d&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[0]]\"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"source-label-container gds-body-s ng-star-inserted\"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-title\" style=\"max-width: 20ch;\">Aiplex Anti-Piracy</span><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p></p><p data-path-to-node=\"1\">Here is how those two phases typically work:</p><h3 data-path-to-node=\"2\">1. Sourcing the Content (The \"Rip\")</h3><p data-path-to-node=\"3\" id=\"p-rc_c61cc9533ace422d-20\"><span class=\"citation-24 citation-end-24\">Before a movie can be pirated, someone has to obtain a digital copy.<source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c213414374=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c213414374=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"2\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span> <span class=\"citation-23 citation-end-23\">Pirates use a few different methods depending on where the movie is currently being shown:<source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c213414374=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c213414374=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"3\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3754498845=\"\">  <source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3754498845=\"\" _nghost-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"></source-inline-chip></sources-carousel-inline></p><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container luminous-sources hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button multiple-button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"Genaue Quellenangaben für Zitate aus Aiplex Anti-Piracy und Edgroom ansehen. Öffnet die Seitenleiste.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_5f824f32d3c5e2d6&quot;,&quot;c_3721b541fcdb6876&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c61cc9533ace422d&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[0]]\"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"source-label-container gds-body-s ng-star-inserted\"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-title\" style=\"max-width: 20ch;\">Aiplex Anti-Piracy</span><span _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-count ng-star-inserted\">+&nbsp;1</span><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p></p><ul data-path-to-node=\"4\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"4,0,0\" id=\"p-rc_c61cc9533ace422d-21\"><b data-path-to-node=\"4,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span class=\"citation-22 citation-end-22\">Camcording (CAM / TS):<source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c213414374=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c213414374=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"4\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></b><span class=\"citation-21 citation-end-21\"> For movies currently only in theaters, someone will physically sneak a camera or smartphone into a theater to record the screen.<source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c213414374=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c213414374=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"5\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span> A \"Telesync\" (TS) is a slightly higher-quality version of this, sometimes using a direct audio connection from headphones meant for the hearing-impaired to get clearer sound.<sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3754498845=\"\">  <source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3754498845=\"\" _nghost-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"></source-inline-chip></sources-carousel-inline></p><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container luminous-sources hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button multiple-button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"Genaue Quellenangaben für Zitate aus Edgroom und Edgroom ansehen. Öffnet die Seitenleiste.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_5f824f32d3c5e2d6&quot;,&quot;c_3721b541fcdb6876&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c61cc9533ace422d&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[0]]\"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"source-label-container gds-body-s ng-star-inserted\"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-title\" style=\"max-width: 20ch;\">Edgroom</span><span _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-count ng-star-inserted\">+&nbsp;1</span><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p></p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"4,1,0\" id=\"p-rc_c61cc9533ace422d-22\"><b data-path-to-node=\"4,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span class=\"citation-20 citation-end-20\">Digital Ripping (Web-DL / WebRip):<source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c213414374=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c213414374=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"6\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></b><span class=\"citation-19 citation-end-19\"> When a movie is released on legitimate streaming services (like Netflix, Disney+, or digital rental platforms), pirates use specialized software to bypass the platform's Digital Rights Management (DRM) encryption.<source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c213414374=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c213414374=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"7\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span> They download the raw video stream directly from the server (Web-DL) or record the screen as it plays back in high definition (WebRip).<sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3754498845=\"\">  <source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3754498845=\"\" _nghost-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"></source-inline-chip></sources-carousel-inline></p><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container luminous-sources hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button multiple-button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"Genaue Quellenangaben für Zitate aus Aiplex Anti-Piracy und Aiplex Anti-Piracy ansehen. Öffnet die Seitenleiste.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_5f824f32d3c5e2d6&quot;,&quot;c_3721b541fcdb6876&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c61cc9533ace422d&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[0]]\"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"source-label-container gds-body-s ng-star-inserted\"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-title\" style=\"max-width: 20ch;\">Aiplex Anti-Piracy</span><span _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-count ng-star-inserted\">+&nbsp;1</span><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p></p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"4,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"4,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Disc Ripping (BDRip / BluRay):</b> Once a movie is released on physical media like Blu-ray or 4K Ultra HD discs, pirates use decryption software to bypass the copy protections on the disc and copy the high-quality video files directly to a computer.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"4,3,0\" id=\"p-rc_c61cc9533ace422d-23\"><span class=\"citation-18\"></span><b data-path-to-node=\"4,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span class=\"citation-18\">Studio Leaks / Screeners (DVDSCR / DVD):</span></b><span class=\"citation-18 citation-end-18\"> Occasionally, promotional copies sent to movie critics, award voters, or industry insiders (screeners) are leaked online.<source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c213414374=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c213414374=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"8\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3754498845=\"\">  <source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3754498845=\"\" _nghost-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"></source-inline-chip></sources-carousel-inline></p><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container luminous-sources hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button multiple-button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"Genaue Quellenangaben für Zitat aus Edgroom ansehen. Öffnet die Seitenleiste.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_5f824f32d3c5e2d6&quot;,&quot;c_3721b541fcdb6876&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c61cc9533ace422d&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[0]]\"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"source-label-container gds-body-s ng-star-inserted\"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-title\" style=\"max-width: 20ch;\">Edgroom</span><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p></p></li></ul><h3 data-path-to-node=\"5\">2. Distribution (The Sharing)</h3><p data-path-to-node=\"6\">Once a pirate has the digital file, they compress it into a smaller file size (often using formats like MKV or MP4) while trying to retain as much visual quality as possible. They then distribute it using a few common methods:</p><ul data-path-to-node=\"7\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" id=\"p-rc_c61cc9533ace422d-24\"><b data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Peer-to-Peer (P2P) Networks / Torrenting:</b> This is the most common method for downloading files. <span class=\"citation-17 citation-end-17\">Using the BitTorrent protocol, a file is broken down into thousands of tiny pieces.<source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c213414374=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c213414374=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"9\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span> <span class=\"citation-16 citation-end-16\">Instead of downloading the whole movie from a single central server, users download pieces of the movie from dozens of other users (peers) who already have them.<source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c213414374=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c213414374=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"10\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span> Once all the pieces are downloaded, the software reassembles them into the full movie.<sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3754498845=\"\">  <source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3754498845=\"\" _nghost-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"></source-inline-chip></sources-carousel-inline></p><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container luminous-sources hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button multiple-button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"Genaue Quellenangaben für Zitate aus Edgroom und Aiplex Anti-Piracy ansehen. Öffnet die Seitenleiste.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_5f824f32d3c5e2d6&quot;,&quot;c_3721b541fcdb6876&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c61cc9533ace422d&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[0]]\"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"source-label-container gds-body-s ng-star-inserted\"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-title\" style=\"max-width: 20ch;\">Edgroom</span><span _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-count ng-star-inserted\">+&nbsp;1</span><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p></p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" id=\"p-rc_c61cc9533ace422d-25\"><b data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Illegal Streaming Sites:</b> Many users prefer not to download files. <span class=\"citation-15 citation-end-15\">Instead, operators of pirate websites upload the ripped movie files to cyberlockers (file-hosting servers) and embedded video players on websites that mimic the look of legitimate streaming platforms.<source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c213414374=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c213414374=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"11\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span> These sites usually make money by flooding the user with intrusive advertisements or malware.<sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3754498845=\"\">  <source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3754498845=\"\" _nghost-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"></source-inline-chip></sources-carousel-inline></p><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container luminous-sources hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button multiple-button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"Genaue Quellenangaben für Zitat aus Aiplex Anti-Piracy ansehen. Öffnet die Seitenleiste.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_5f824f32d3c5e2d6&quot;,&quot;c_3721b541fcdb6876&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c61cc9533ace422d&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[0]]\"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"source-label-container gds-body-s ng-star-inserted\"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-title\" style=\"max-width: 20ch;\">Aiplex Anti-Piracy</span><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p></p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"7,2,0\" id=\"p-rc_c61cc9533ace422d-26\"><span class=\"citation-14\"></span><b data-path-to-node=\"7,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span class=\"citation-14\">Direct Downloads and Cyberlockers:</span></b><span class=\"citation-14 citation-end-14\"> Files are uploaded to cloud storage or file-hosting services where users can download the entire file via a direct link.<source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c213414374=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c213414374=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"12\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3754498845=\"\">  <source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3754498845=\"\" _nghost-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"></source-inline-chip></sources-carousel-inline></p><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container luminous-sources hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button multiple-button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"Genaue Quellenangaben für Zitat aus Reddit ansehen. Öffnet die Seitenleiste.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_5f824f32d3c5e2d6&quot;,&quot;c_3721b541fcdb6876&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c61cc9533ace422d&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[0]]\"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"source-label-container gds-body-s ng-star-inserted\"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-title\" style=\"max-width: 20ch;\">Reddit</span><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p></p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"7,3,0\" id=\"p-rc_c61cc9533ace422d-27\"><span class=\"citation-13\"></span><b data-path-to-node=\"7,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span class=\"citation-13\">Social Media and Chat Apps:</span></b><span class=\"citation-13 citation-end-13\"> Increasingly, pirated content is shared in private channels or groups on platforms like Telegram, Discord, or dedicated subreddits.<source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c213414374=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c213414374=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"13\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3754498845=\"\">  <source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3754498845=\"\" _nghost-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"></source-inline-chip></sources-carousel-inline></p><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container luminous-sources hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button multiple-button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"Genaue Quellenangaben für Zitat aus Aiplex Anti-Piracy ansehen. Öffnet die Seitenleiste.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_5f824f32d3c5e2d6&quot;,&quot;c_3721b541fcdb6876&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c61cc9533ace422d&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[0]]\"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"source-label-container gds-body-s ng-star-inserted\"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1722658458=\"\" class=\"source-title\" style=\"max-width: 20ch;\">Aiplex Anti-Piracy</span><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----></button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p></p></li></ul><h3 data-path-to-node=\"9\">How the Industry Fights Back</h3><p data-path-to-node=\"10\">Because piracy costs the entertainment industry billions of dollars annually, studios and tech companies use several countermeasures:</p><ul data-path-to-node=\"11\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Digital Watermarking:</b> Studios embed invisible identifiers into theater prints or digital screeners. If a copy leaks, they can trace exactly which theater or individual reviewer it came from.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Automated Takedowns:</b> Anti-piracy firms use AI and automated bots to scan torrent sites, Google search results, and social media for copyrighted titles, issuing immediate digital takedown notices (DMCA requests).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"11,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">ISP Blocking:</b> In many countries, internet service providers are legally required to block access to known piracy and torrent tracking domains.</p></li></ul>"
    },
